  • public abstract class PrimaryExpression
extends Expression
    Abstract placeholder class for parsing primary expressions.

    EBNF definition:
    PRIMARY_EXPRESSION = IDENTIFIER_EXPRESSION | INTEGER_LITERAL_EXPRESSION | "(" EXPRESSION ")"
